query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_properties,
  COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) as unique_properties,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM properties WHERE id IN (SELECT DISTINCT property_id FROM property_images)) as properties_with_images,
  COUNT(DISTINCT pi.property_id) as properties_with_at_least_one_image
FROM properties p
LEFT JOIN property_images pi ON p.id = pi.property_id;
